{"tid":545323,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[是日晚餐] 自制咖喱雞飯","createTime":"2018-01-30T11:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T07:05:58.000Z","uid":43041,"like":85,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a27ea55dbd6d803bc3af24a5da2148ac636c9fb3","tid":545323,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/nzFjom/IMG_20180130_183012.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FnzFjom%2FIMG_20180130_183012.jpg&h=10e226f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n洋蔥切片蒜蓉切碎，攪混咖喱粉：<br />\nground coriander<br />\nground cumin<br />\nturmeric<br />\npaprika<br />\nsalt<br />\ncayenne pepper<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/dKB1ZR/IMG_20180130_183113.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FdKB1ZR%2FIMG_20180130_183113.jpg&h=8bd94a90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拎一半粉出黎同雞攪混，醃幾個字<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/d33R16/IMG_20180130_183217.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2Fd33R16%2FIMG_20180130_183217.jpg&h=f619b553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n醃好就落油炒香<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/b19c8m/IMG_20180130_183309.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2Fb19c8m%2FIMG_20180130_183309.jpg&h=e6eee2de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n變金黃色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拎出黎擺埋一邊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/hWoFuR/IMG_20180130_183416.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FhWoFuR%2FIMG_20180130_183416.jpg&h=eebed76d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用炒雞剩低既油炒洋蔥至透明<br />\n然後落埋剩低既咖喱混合粉同蒜蓉炒香<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/hrkTER/IMG_20180130_183530.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FhrkTER%2FIMG_20180130_183530.jpg&h=309d9718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n倒入雞湯，再加少量茄汁同花生醬攪混<br />\n煮到自己鐘意既燶杰度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/fN61ZR/IMG_20180130_183708.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FfN61ZR%2FIMG_20180130_183708.jpg&h=fc160653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完成"},{"pid":"53c71b0e633964d3f05e45cc2a8672f90613f1f8","tid":545323,"uid":76757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:50:53.000Z","msg":"好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ef1ef0a5a4f3d96fe924a2059c8a14a9c3c727","tid":545323,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:56:11.000Z","msg":"8.5/10"},{"pid":"a2c49fbb7873a8db3adae51e9a3d9a72735a1e95","tid":545323,"uid":43041,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"53c71b0e633964d3f05e45cc2a8672f90613f1f8","tid":545323,"uid":76757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:50:53.000Z","msg":"好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:56:44.000Z","msg":"過黎姐姐請你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8ca7bd45274d1d18bf12353b5f7f54e7db48e0","tid":545323,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96ef1ef0a5a4f3d96fe924a2059c8a14a9c3c727","tid":545323,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:56:11.000Z","msg":"8.5/10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:59:08.000Z","msg":"好高分 多謝<br />\n有無咩建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0f86f3e484459aaf800468fe673d3c282f8393","tid":545323,"uid":163107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T12:05:46.000Z","msg":"點解要加番茄汁同花生醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cab6fe71e2e3fab1b6480a4deb87a00aaf4dfdb","tid":545323,"uid":36178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T12:07:38.000